<div class="content"><p>This document specifies the Remote Authorization API
Protocol. The Remote Authorization API Protocol is a Remote Procedure Call
(RPC)-based protocol used to perform various authorization queries on remote
computers.</p><p>Sections 1.5, 1.8, 1.9, 2, and 3 of this specification are
normative. All other sections and examples in this specification are
informative.</p></div>